## Captioned Images

```css
:root {
  --image-caption-align: left;
  --image-caption-font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
  --image-title-align: left;
}
```

::: style --image-caption-align: left; --image-caption-font-size: var(--font-size-xs); --image-title-align: left;

```html raw
<stencila-image-object content-url="https://placehold.co/600x360/93c5fd/1f2937?text=Image">
  <img src="https://placehold.co/600x360/93c5fd/1f2937?text=Image" />
  <span slot="title">Figure title</span>
  <span slot="caption">A brief caption describing the image content.</span>
</stencila-image-object>
```

:::

## Inline Images

Inline images align with surrounding text and scale to the line height:

```css
:root {
  /* No design token overrides */
}
```

::: style

The icon ![](https://placehold.co/24x24/93c5fd/1f2937?text=+) appears inline with text.

:::
